snippet.textDisplay: I am a girl of a normal middle class brown family and I'm the middle child who is always expected to be strong. From my childhood I've been taught to protect my sister like a bodyguard, teach my brother like a teacher and excel because my parents expect everything from me. And there are times when I feel completely blank about life. I know mujh life m kya krna h but there sometimes is no hope. It feels like the walls are closing in you have to pretend and pretend that everything is fine while performing your duties and amidst all that I have to stand strong when I know I can't for long, this song gives me that power to stand strong. I've been listening to Talha Anjum for a while now, and I always loved how he describes life. But this song is different. I literally get goosebumps and tears while listening to this track. Thankyou so much for creating magic ✨
